snippet.title: Spy Fiction
snippet.description:
This is the official trailer for the game Spy Fiction. Developped by Access Games (a studio created by Toru Fujiwara from Makaimura, Tomba! & Bio Hazard fame) and published by Sammy, this game is a stealth action game with some cool ideas (some ideas are borrowed from Metal Gear Solid 2 others can be found in Metal Gear Solid 3 but Spy Fiction predate MGS3 by one year).

The game character design is done by Range Murata (Wachenroder, Last Exile, Goketsuji Ichizoku)
